-- Ford reports sales fell 48 percent
-- 
-- Tue Mar 3, 2009 12:16pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/03/03/us-ford-idUSTRE52253220090303

 

 (Reuters) - Ford Motor Co ( F.N ) reports February sales fell  48.4 percent. The company says February inventories totaled 405,000 vehicles and it plans to produce 425,000 vehicles in Q2. 

